snippet.title: Warhammer 40,000: Battlesector - Official Update Overview Trailer
snippet.description:
Get a deep dive into recent updates available for Warhammer 40,000: Battlesector, as well as a peek at what's in the works for the strategy game. The team at Slitherine also gives us a look at three new units available today with the latest update for the game, including the Royal Warden (Necrons), Biovore (Tyranids), and Pyrovore (Tyranids). Finally, check out the reveal that the Astra Militarum faction is coming in the future as part of a new DLC expansion.

#IGN #Gaming
